The point of this isnt that you just play it, you import characters (I made 3 so far) into this and share a sanctuary during a zombie breakout. 

I'm proooobably going to workshop the story to be less blatantly self indulging eventually but this is what I've gotten so far.

Long story short, there's a magical barrier that is basically fueled by you fucking the chicks that are there with you keeping the zombies out.

Am going to eventually have it track statistics better to make it feel more like an actual survival game.
